@using BestNox;
@* トップページ *@
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = SystemConstants.Title;
}
<div class="header-blue">
    <div class="container hero">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 col-xl-5 offset-xl-1">
                <h1>We work for the money.</h1>
                <p>Getting money is to provide value to people. There is no value for simple work. We eliminate simple tasks.<br><br>Even if the common people despise us, we will not step back. That is the BestNox.</p><button class="btn btn-light btn-lg action-button"
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  type="button">
                    Learn More
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5 col-lg-5 offset-lg-1 offset-xl-0 d-none d-lg-block phone-holder">
                <div class="iphone-mockup">
                    <img class="device" src="~/images/iphone.svg">
                    <div class="screen"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="features-blue">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="intro">
            <h2 class="text-center">Features</h2>
            <p class="text-center">Our service is unbeatable!<br>It is a strong force that can change even desperate destiny!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="row features">
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 item">
                <i class="fa fa-map-marker icon"></i>
                <h3 class="name">Unlimited environment</h3>
                <p class="description">Our company has introduced the latest working environment. You can work without choosing time or place. This is very useful for workers.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 item">
                <i class="fa fa-clock-o icon"></i>
                <h3 class="name">Strong insurance</h3>
                <p class="description">Even if you get hit by a truck, you can incarnate into another world depending on the judgment of the gods. At this time, you will be able to use some cheats.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 item">
                <i class="fa fa-list-alt icon"></i>
                <h3 class="name">Future tools</h3>
                <p class="description">A mysterious robot will come to your room from a distant future. He will take out a strange tool from the pocket on his body and fulfill your wish.<br></p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 item">
                <i class="fa fa-flash icon"></i>
                <h3 class="name">Amazing power</h3>
                <p class="description">Consuming 24 points of magic power can inflict 156 to 172 damage to all enemies. This is a large value that can not be tolerated by the general public.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 item">
                <i class="fa fa-plane icon"></i>
                <h3 class="name">Send to hell</h3>
                <p class="description">You can send your opponent to hell instantly. However, the person who used also goes to hell after death. He has to wander in the darkness forever, with pain and suffering.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 item">
                <i class="fa fa-heart icon"></i>
                <h3 class="name">Transformable</h3>
                <p class="description">If you have a kind heart to protect your friends, you can be transformed into a legendary warrior.<br>(women only)</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="projects-clean">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="intro">
            <h2 class="text-center">Projects </h2>
            <p class="text-center">We can use the sacred and powerful techniques to revive even the dying world. It is a future technology that solves problems that were thought to be impossible until now! </p>
        </div>
        <div class="row projects">
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4 item">
                <img class="img-fluid" src="~/images/desk.jpg">
                <h3 class="name">Educational software</h3>
                <p class="description">
                    There is a lot of waste and no freedom in the educational setting. Because teachers in the country teach the same contents to each student.<br><br>Using this system, students can review videos that they are not good at repeatedly.
                    In addition, teachers can be devoted to helping students.<br><br>Even a busy office worker or an unskilled old man can learn specializedly at any time they like and expand their potential.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4 item">
                <img class="img-fluid" src="~/images/building.jpg">
                <h3 class="name">Voting system</h3>
                <p class="description">
                    The current voting system has many shortcomings and needs improvement. Since the voting destination is described by hand, counting errors and counterfeiting may occur. Since voting takes analog and time-consuming methods, it is expensive
                    and difficult to confirm the will of the people.<br><br>There have been various debates over this issue concerning computerization. However, it has been denied because it is a problem when hacked by a technician.<br><br>By making
                    full use of P2P technology, it is possible to introduce a tamper-proof data system. We will be able to vote more familiar and accurate than ever before.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4 item">
                <img class="img-fluid" src="~/images/loft.jpg">
                <h3 class="name">Beating Furniture</h3>
                <p class="description">
                    In recent years, small-scale housing and furniture for singles have been actively provided. But it is not enough just to protect your mind from loneliness.<br><br>We need someone to greet me in the morning, and someone to wait for
                    the return from work.<br><br>The magical furniture we offer will learn about you like a living being. It imitates the voice of your ideal male or female image and keeps you away from loneliness.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
