            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 item">
                <img class="rounded-circle" src="~/images/tango.png">
                <h3 class="name">Tango Kerberos</h3>
                <p class="title">EXPLORER</p>
                <p class="description">
                    He has explored so many ruins and excavated treasures so far. He decided to join the organization to take advantage of the adventurer's intuition. Because his ability is worthwhile to be used by someone. He has known that his experience
